			<tr>
				<td width="100%"><a href="viewtopic.php?p=20846&amp;sid=1bc0a61eb814ba513e133878bdeff062#20846"><img src="templates/ashGrunge/images/icon_minipost.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" border="0" /></a><span class="postdetails">Posted: 12.05 03.06pm<span class="gen">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;Post subject: How do you guys raid? What general rules should I follow?</span></td>
				<td valign="top" align="right" nowrap="nowrap"><a href="posting.php?mode=quote&amp;p=20846&amp;sid=1bc0a61eb814ba513e133878bdeff062"><img src="templates/ashGrunge/images/lang_english/icon_quote.gif" alt="Reply with quote" title="Reply with quote" border="0" /></a>   </td>
